Parameter.description: Represents the property information for all discs.

ComponentEvent.Notes: DISCPROP DISCPROP-<key>,<value> Disc properties query changed, responds with multiple DISCPROP-<key>,<value> commands, one for each key

DISCINFO DISCINFO-<num>,<duration>,<total­Titles>,<totalTracks>,<disc­Type>,<id> Disc info changed, where <num> is disc number, <duration> is a disc duration String in the format [-]hh:mm:ss.ff, <# of tracks> is the number of titles in this disc, <# of tracks> is the number of tracks in this disc, <disctype> is the disc type (AUDIO_ONLY, VIDEO_ONLY, AUDIOVIDEO) and <id> is the disc database id.

TITLEINFO TITLEINFO-<num>,<duration>,<# of tracks>,<discNumber> Title info changed, where <num> is title number, <duration> is a title duration String in the format [-]hh:mm:ss.ff, <# of tracks> is the number of tracks in this title and <disc­Number> is the disc number the title belongs to.
TITLECOUNTERNOTIFY-<state> Turn title counter notification on or off, where <state> is 1 or 0
